metadata.name: Scarlet Kiss
metadata.description: The play of light and shadow, harsh and soft, on the tulip petal drew my attention. I looked through the lens and saw the petal-like a stiff wooden plank coming into the light but a softness with the raindrops and shadow.

attributes.value: Sony a7r2 - ISO 400 - f/8.0 - 1/400thSony FE Macro 90mm F/2.8 G OSS
